18.10	Katamon	Katamon	Katamon (Arabic: ‎, Hebrew: ‎) is a neighbourhood in south-central Jerusalem, Israel. The official Hebrew name, Gonen (Hebrew: ‎‎), is only used in municipal publications. Katamon is derived from the Greek kata tōi monastēriōi ("below the monastery").	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/San_Simon_Monastery_1.jpg/250px-San_Simon_Monastery_1.jpg
